15 C. 1. Students who are guilty of any of the following acts may
16 be suspended out-of-school by the administration of the school or
17 district:
18 a. violation of a school regulation,
19 b. possession of an intoxicating beverage, low-point
20 beer, as defined by Section 163.2 1-103 of Title 37
21 37A of the Oklahoma Statutes, or missing or stolen
22 property if the property is reasonably suspected to
23 have been taken from a student, a school employee, or
24 the school during school activities, and
